                                    </imageobject>
                                </inlinemediaobject>
                                -->
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </para>
            </sect3>
    
            <sect3>
                <title>Fields</title>
                <para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>
                                <emphasis role="bold">Modules</emphasis> - The list of modules you want to search across.
                                <itemizedlist>
                                    <listitem>
                                        <para>
                                            <emphasis role="bold">(de)select all</emphasis> (Optional) - Selects or Deselects all of the modules.
                                        </para>
                                    </listitem>
                                </itemizedlist>
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><emphasis role="bold">Component</emphasis> (Optional) - The name of the component you want to search across.</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>
                                <emphasis role="bold">Event Id</emphasis> (Optional) - The Event Id of a specific event you are looking.
                                <emphasis role="bold">NOTE:</emphasis> This is not the wiretap event id, it is the actual event id. 
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>
                                <emphasis role="bold">From</emphasis> (Optional) - The from part of the date/time range to search across.
                                If your browser has Javascript enabled then a helpful Date Picker pops up when you enter this field.
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>
                                <emphasis role="bold">Until</emphasis> (Optional) - The until part of the date/time range to search across.
                                If your browser has Javascript enabled then a helpful Date Picker pops up when you enter this field.
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><emphasis role="bold">Payload Content</emphasis> (Optional) - A free form search criteria for data inside a payload.  <emphasis role="bold">WARNING:</emphasis> this can slow down the search significantly.</para>
                        </listitem>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>
                                <emphasis role="bold">Order By</emphasis> (Optional) - What the search results should be ordered by.
                                <itemizedlist>
                                    <listitem>
                                        <para>
                                            <emphasis role="bold">Ascending</emphasis> (Optional) - Whether the search results should be displayed in Ascending or Descending order.
                                        </para>
                                    </listitem>
                                </itemizedlist>
                            </para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </para>
            </sect3>
    
            <sect3>
                <title>Actions</title>
                <para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para><emphasis role="bold">Search for Events</emphasis> - Executes the search based on the Search Criteria given.</para>
                        </listitem>
                    </itemizedlist>
                </para>
            </sect3>

            <sect3>
                <title>Errors</title>
                <para>
                    <itemizedlist>
                        <listitem>
                            <para>
                                If you provide an incorrect username and/or password then the 
                                following error is displayed:
                                <!--
                                <inlinemediaobject>
